title: Independent candidate Akhtar Khan wins PK-05 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 9 (APP): Independent candidate Akhtar Khan has won the election for Khyber Pakhtunkhwa Assembly constituency PK-05 Swat-III by securing 24,055 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Sanaullah Khan of JUI-P who bagged 15,462 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turnout remained 41.34 per cent.
